snippet.title: Juggler for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

In Juggler you have to keep various items from falling on the ground, or else you lose 1 life. 

You get bonus points if you manage to "juggle" the items to the right of the screen.


What I think:

Fun and challening game, that also gets repetitive.
